data.description: West Sherman area in quiet and well established neighborhood with mature trees and a porte-cache on front of home.  This 4 bedroom 2 bath home offers large rooms, 2 living areas, secluded backyard, galley kitchen and so much more!  Within minutes of retail, dining, medical and schools, close to the new Texas IT Corridor.  Easy access to 1417, Hwy 289, Hwy's 56,75 and 82.  Forgive the clutter, in the middle of thinning out and packing.  With all of this home on one level this is very accommodating. Small back porch to secluded area with a small storage shed tucked in back on the side, out of site.  Phenomenal fauna with mature plants, vines and trees.   Roof replaced March 2023, this is a very well maintained home.  Shows to be partial 100 year flood plane.    Appt must be made to see, see agent notes for times.  Buyer to verify all.
